# Cursor Rules — tw-trading-unified

You are working on a Taiwan futures + options trading system. Bugs cause real financial loss.

## Mandatory
- Read RULES.md before any change
- Run `python3 -m pytest tests/ -v` before and after changes
- Never write side effects (CSV, log) before validating the operation
- PaperTrader.position is the single source of truth for position state
- All PnL must include fees and tax
- Stop loss >= 10 pts (covers round-trip cost)
- Paper mode capital limit: 40,000 TWD

## Don't
- Don't use `from datetime import datetime` in files needing `datetime.timedelta`
- Don't maintain position state in multiple places
- Don't show gross PnL without deducting costs
- Don't skip margin checks in paper mode
